    23→
    24→Plain paragraph for rich message smoke.
    25→- List A
    26→- List B
    27→| Column A | Column B |
    28→| --- | --- |
    29→| 1 | 2 |
    30→
    31→\`\`\`ts
    32→const ok = true;
    33→\`\`\`
    34→
    35→:::unknown
    36→Unsupported extension block should pass through unchanged.`);
